  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "HK USC .45 ACP 卡宾枪",
      "en": "HK USC .45 ACP carbine"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "USC",
      "en": "USC"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "USC（通用半自动卡宾枪）是UMP的纯半自动版本，专为民用市场设计。该枪诞生于1994年美国《突击武器禁令》颁布后，并于2000年正式推出。相较于原版UMP的主要改动包括：采用拇指孔式枪托/握把替代手枪式握把、延长枪管并取消消焰器、弹匣容量限制为10发，以及采用纯半自动击发机构与枪机组件。",
      "en": "The USC or Universal Self-loading Carbine is a semi-automatic-only variant of the UMP designed for civilian use. It was created following the Assault Weapons Ban of 1994 in the United States and was introduced in 2000. Changes from the original UMP include a thumbhole type stock/grip instead of the pistol grip of the UMP, a longer barrel without the flash suppressor, a magazine limited to 10 rounds, and a semi-automatic-only trigger group and action."
    },
